{"tid":2085164,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"想學好英文, 諗住為去外國打工作準備","createTime":"2020-06-29T17:05:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-29T17:32:35.000Z","uid":262274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"4cc1c96e47a8e1db7cd609065e474db33fca8b97","tid":2085164,"uid":262274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T17:05:03.000Z","msg":"小弟97年出世老豆老母有幫我申請BNO, 英國似乎會比BNO工作簽證, 打算做幾年野睇下有冇機會攞BC。不過細過返學睇到英文就頭暈, 一直冇落心機去學, 英文水平都幾差下。依家國安法殺到埋嚟, 我自己比較悲觀, 覺得香港應該玩完, 所以想惡補返啲英文。<br />\n<br />\n自己有諗過用持續進修基金去讀, 不過唔知揀邊間學英文好。所以想睇下大家有咩意見。<br />\n<br />\n我知有人一定講去到嗰度做野慢慢就識講, 不過都想打好個底, 無謂去到嗰度雞同鴨講。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7eebd9983d398945a0e68c41ecc466115911bee","tid":2085164,"uid":53524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T17:05:36.000Z","msg":"China Town"},{"pid":"b347f07748dd10bdcfd46d4678d94216e32ce9f7","tid":2085164,"uid":262274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f7eebd9983d398945a0e68c41ecc466115911bee","tid":2085164,"uid":53524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T17:05:36.000Z","msg":"China Town"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T17:06:55.000Z","msg":"想融入當地社會, 唔想圍爐。China Town怕自己一放工就講中文"},{"pid":"b4ad2854f17f4423a4d9f3106c1c49780a74c8dc","tid":2085164,"uid":262274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T17:10:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/sneeze.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d71b6596f60be9b44311bf8ed805d1af77ea69b","tid":2085164,"uid":351574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b347f07748dd10bdcfd46d4678d94216e32ce9f7","tid":2085164,"uid":262274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f7eebd9983d398945a0e68c41ecc466115911bee","tid":2085164,"uid":53524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T17:05:36.000Z","msg":"China Town"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-29